title: BMW Road Map Europe PREMIUM WEST 2016-1 1 USB Version
description:
BMW Road Map Europe PREMIUM WEST 2016-1 - 1 USB Original Version


Enjoy updating your maps to the latest 2016 version.

Why is this version the easiest and best? Because you will just need
one USB Stick, no need for 3 sticks or other complicated methods.


------------------------------------------------------------------
For FSC Activation Code contact us at the address found in the 
instructions.txt and send us your VIN number (last 7 characters).

Our price is lower than anyone else`s on the market.
------------------------------------------------------------------

You will need a 32GB USB Stick Fat32 formatted to copy the files and plug it in the glove box usb port of the car, then press Start update on your Idrive. You will need to input the activation code to start the update process. The code is specific to each individual car and won`t work only for the car it has been requested for.
